---
title: Grilled Spicy Caribbean Chicken Salad  with Jerk Sweet Potatoes and Corn
description: This salad is bringing the Island flavour. Corn, roasted sweet potato and crunchy cucumbers are tossed in a creamy sriracha dressing, then eaten with a spicy Jerk seasoned chicken for a meal that truly kicks things up a notch.
